Params: {1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/Bgstory88.png'}
{2: '??', 3: 'Hey! You there!'}
{1: '1', 3: 'A man with an electromagnetic harpoon gun appears from the side of a container.'}
{2: 'Fisher', 3: 'Do you know what we do to trespassers?', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: "We're the Gray Ravens from Babylonia. I'm their leader, Lucia.", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Fisher', 3: 'Pff, like I give a... Babylonia, you say?', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Fisher', 3: "Fine, the Captain's Council has informed us that representatives from Babylonia can be released on account of trade.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Fisher', 3: 'That being said, whatever you fish flakes do...', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Fisher', 3: 'Keep your grubby little fins out of our business, ya hear? Now, follow me!', 4: '1'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/Bgstory92.png'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Fisher', 3: 'Alright, wait here on the dock!', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Fisher', 3: "After your transport craft takes you back to space, don't you ever show your faces here again.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Fisher', 3: "Huh? Something's goin' on over there. I'm gonna go check it out. Remember to mind your own business.", 4: '1'}
{3: 'On the dock not far away is a group of people causing a commotion.'}
{1: '1', 3: "Rosetta's tall body towers over the crowd, while Evan, who is leaning against her legs, is buried in the crowd."}
{1: '1', 2: 'Sailor', 3: "You're here for that Narwhal again, aren't you?", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Sailor', 3: 'Whenever that blasted Narwhal shows up, he always messes up the port.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Sailor', 3: "And you, Forest Guard. You're a criminal who was expelled for breaking the rules...", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Sailor', 3: 'Yet you continue to violate them by coming back here and defending this damn Narwhal!', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Sailor', 3: 'With that thing of yours...', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 3: 'Rosetta glances at the lance in her hand.'}
{2: 'Sailor', 3: "You should've been using that lance to protect our borders...", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Sailor', 3: 'On the contrary, while the entire port is under threat from the Corrupted...', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Sailor', 3: "You come to cause us more troubles with that Narwhal... It's a joke to place our hope on the loyalty of you Forest Guards...", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Evan', 3: "Don't you know? Rosetta always comes to soothe Derek and make him leave! And she even clears up all the Corrupted!", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Evan', 3: "And the Forest Guards have worked hard to protect the southern forest all these years. Even if you don't like them, they've always given it their all!", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Evan', 3: "You just didn't see it!", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Sailor', 3: 'You little runt! Always sneaking out!', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Evan', 3: "Miss Rosetta, you're going to help us clean up the Corrupted this time, won't you?", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Sailor', 3: "Stubborn brat, remember what we've taught you?", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Sailor', 3: 'The most important thing for us in the ARU is our loyalty to the collective and our homeland.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Sailor', 3: "From the day of the outbreak, we've been protecting our homeland ourselves. We do not tolerate betrayal.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Sailor', 3: 'Traitors are not trustworthy, and so are the robots corrupted by the Punishing Virus!', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: 'Hmph... That sure is an unpleasant thing to hear.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 3: 'Rosetta stands there in silence, showing no sign of wavering.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Fisher', 3: "Don't just stand there! Crawl back to your forest!", 4: '1'}
{3: 'The port citizens point their weapons at Rosetta.'}
{2: 'Citizen', 3: 'Yeah! Go back to your forest!'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: 'Commandant, do you think we should get involved?', 4: '1'}
{2: '(Interfere)', 3: '79', 4: '(Watch and wait)', 5: '80'}
{2: 'Lucia', 3: "I'll handle this.", 4: '1'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/Bgstory86.png'}
{3: 'Right then, the ocean surface near the port begins to surge...'}
{3: 'A colossal Narwhal breaches the surface and thrashes in the sea. Massive waves begin to rock the boats berthed in the port.'}
